John, that sounds like a potential bug.  Can you find in the code where the=
 mutate_add_link and mutate_add_node methods are called?  You should be abl=
e to see the condition it is checking to decide whether to call them.  That=
 will tell you if the variable in question is the only factor in the condit=
ion.  If it is, then it is possible that the variable itself is not being r=
eset properly through the GUI, which you can check by outputting the variab=
le when the condition is checked.  

ken
